" set guifont=Ricty\ for\ Powerline\ 10
set guioptions=eg
" e is smart tab bar
" I don't know what g mean...orz
" m is menubar
" T is toolbar
" r and R is right scrollbar
" l and L is left scrollbar
" b is bottom scrollbar
